pullRequest.body:
This PR adds a variant of a lemma introduced in #8512: `ShortComplex.SnakeInput.Î´_apply'` computes the connecting homomorphism of the snake lemma in a concrete categoriy `C` with a phrasing based on the functor `forgetâ‚‚ C Ab` rather than `forget C`. From this, the lemma `ShortComplex.ShortExact.Î´_apply` is obtained in a new file `Algebra.Homology.ConcreteCategory`: it gives a computation in terms of (co)cycles of the connecting homomorphism in homology attached to a short exact sequence of homological complexes in `C`.

This PR also adds a lemma which computes "up to refinements" the connecting homomorphism of the homology sequence in general abelian categories.

---

- [x] depends on: #8468
- [x] depends on: #8765
